name: Brass Locket Earrings
description:
Vintage aged brass locket charms from the 1960s glow against dark oxidized brass chain from the 1970s for a warm distressed look. Place little pictures or keepsakes inside, holding memories near and dear. Super light weight despite their statement making style. 

►Vintage brass locket, oxidized geometric chain
►Hanging 2 1/2 inches long
►Locket charm measures 1/2 inch
►Vintage solid brass french hook ear wires
►Arrives in a stylish hand-decorated kraft gift box

name: Duster Copper Teardrop Earrings
description:
Tiny cream colored swirl lucite beads offset long slender vintage copper teardrop charms from the 1970s layered with a strand of delicate vintage dark oxidized brass geometric chain. So airy and light yet full of texture and detail, they'll surely catch a second glance. 

►Lucite beads from the 1960s
►1970s copper teardrop drops
►Oxidized brass chain
►Vintage solid brass ear hooks
►3 1/2 inches long

name: Fringe Bib Necklace
description:
A vintage bib necklace that is bold and edgy yet delicate and feminine! 1970s copper fringe charms are layered with aged brass points and hanging from vintage copper chain. Available in both long (28 inch) style and shorter (24 inch) style. Thoroughly modern yet 100% vintage. 

►Copper fringe charms
►Brass point charms
►Copper chain 
►Available in 24 or 28 inch length
►Arrives in a beautifully decorated gift box

►►►Featured on FAB.COM!

name: Layered Brass Chain Necklace
description:
Four strands of vintage 1970s chain - from shiny brass to darkly oxidized - are brought together in varied lengths to create a stunning, bold statement necklace. Perfect to pair with everything from a simple T to your Little Black Dress.

►Vintage 1970s brass chain
►24 inches at longest point
►Attached with sturdy napier hook clasps
►Arrives packaged in hand-decorated gift box

name: Tribal Shield Earrings
description:
One of my all-time most popular style earrings are back - with a twist! Gorgeous vintage gunmetal silver shield charms, finished with a filigree brass fan detail are paired with deep jade green lucite beads for a splash of color. Hanging from vintage brass oversized kidney ear hooks, they're even more dramatic and eye-catching.

►1970s gunmetal and brass charms
►Vintage lucite beads
►Vintage 14k gold over brass long kidney ear hooks
►Charm 1 1/2 inches long
►Total length 4 inches long

name: Tassel Hoop Earrings
description:
An eye-catching collection of vintage naturally aged brass hoop charms, brass and copper tassels and jade green glass beads from the 1970s. Full of texture, swing and sway. Super light-weight. 

►Hanging 3 inches long
►Vintage solid brass oversized kidney ear hooks
►Arrives in a hand-decorated gift box

name: Sparkly Spinner Pendant Necklace
description:
A vintage silver base spinning charm necklace from the 1960s holds two sparkling pale peach gemstone cabs in a copper setting. Hangs from a long copper ribbon link chain full of sparkle and shine itself. A stunningly simple piece that makes a bright statement. 

These charms were used much like lockets in the 1970s, to hold pictures of your loved ones near and dear. My Mom had a key chain version of this charm carrying around a toothless 2nd grade school portrait of Glamourpuss herself! 

►Charm pendant measures 1 1/4 inch. 
►Chain measures 24 inches long.
►Packaged in a hand-decorated gift box.

►►►Featured on FAB.COM!

name: Tribal Chevron Necklace
description:
Three graduated strands of vintage brass snake chain hold a layering of brass tube beads and etched white tribal patterned lucite beads from the 1960s. Simple, stylish and right on trend. 

►1970s brass snake chain
►Vintage lucite etched beads
►Solid brass tube beads from the 1970s
►Chain lengths - 20, 24, 26 inches. 
►Arrives beautifully packaged in decorated gift box

name: Aged Leaf Necklace
description:
Gorgeously detailed vintage solid brass leaf charms from the 1960s, naturally aged to different shades of patina, are simply hung from delicate vintage gingerbread patina brass chain. Stunning and simple yet full of ornate detail and charm.

►Solid brass leaf charm
►1970s brass twist link chain
►Chain 24 inches long
►Charm 1 1/2 inches long x 3/4 inch wide

name: Double Loop Hoop Earrings
description:
Hoop earrings, oversized for oompf, with a fringe of copper chain and warm wine lucite beads. 1970s elements come together in thoroughly modern fashion.

►Brass double loop hoop charms
►Bronze chain fringe
►Vintage lucite beads in warm wine
►Vintage brass ear hooks
►4 inches long
►Hoop 1 3/4 inches long by 1 1/2 inches wide

name: Isoceles Dangles Vintage Triangle Earrings
description:
Silver mesh isosceles triangle charms from the 1970s have aged naturally to a beautiful coppery patina. Math never looked so good! 

The geometric trend of the late 70s/early 80s was inspired by the growing technology of the day. Personal computers, cell phones, and video games were making their earliest appearance, lending a 'space aged' theme to fashion. 

►Charm 2 inches x 1 inch across at widest point
►Hanging from solid brass long kidney ear wires
►Total length= 3 inches long
►Arrives in a hand decorated gift box, ready for the giving

*Available in wholesale quantities

name: Tribal Geometric Beaded Necklace
description:
A little bit tribal, a little geometric, all vintage and totally modern! Vintage cream lucite tube beads, butterscotch oval beads and stacked green pebble beads are paired with vintage 1970s brass snake chain and finished with vintage brass geometric point charms.

►Vintage 1960s lucite beads
►1970s brass snake chain
►Vintage brass geometric point charms
►22 inches long (can be adjusted to any length)
►Brass spring ring clasp
►Arrives in a hand-decorated gift box

name: Double Dagger Vintage Brass and Gold Earrings
description:
Vintage 1970s brass dagger charms with a diagonal texture pattern are layered with smaller vintage gold plated charms. Just the right amount of disco glam paired with every day style. 

►1970s brass charms
►Vintage gold plated charms
►Vintage solid brass french hoop ear wires
►1 1/2 inches long
